Implementation guidance:

**Location**: packages/vscode-extension/src/extension.ts in the cairn.editTicket command

**Current behavior**: 
Panel title is set to full task title + ID: `${ticket.title} (#${id})`
Example: "Fix relationship lines rendering for tasks with varying heights in Cairn Issues view (#s-2_XnaRfe)"

**Desired behavior**:
Truncate long titles with ellipsis in the middle, keeping ID visible
Example: "Fix relationship... (#s-2_XnaRfe)"

**Suggested implementation**:
```typescript
function truncateTitle(title: string, id: string, maxLength = 50): string {
  const suffix = ` (#${id})`;
  const maxTitleLength = maxLength - suffix.length;

  if (title.length <= maxTitleLength) {
    return `${title}${suffix}`;
  }

  // Show first part and ellipsis, keeping ID at end
  const truncated = title.substring(0, maxTitleLength - 3) + '...';
  return `${truncated}${suffix}`;
}
```

**Files to modify**:
- extension.ts: Update panel.title assignment in editTicket command (~line where title is set)
- Consider also updating the initial createWebviewPanel call for consistency

**Testing**:
- Open tasks with short titles (< 50 chars) - should show full title
- Open tasks with long titles (> 50 chars) - should truncate with ellipsis
- Verify ID remains visible in all cases
